    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "#### Add SQL Server connection strings\r\nAdd the monitoring config for this virtual machine. It involves providing a set of connection strings for the SQL databases you would like to monitor. \r\n\r\nNote that you have the option to define parameters to reference secrets from an Azure Key Vault or for just reuse of tokens across connection strings. [Learn more](https://github.com/acearun/managedsolutions/blob/master/Documentation/Workloads/sql-configs.md)."
      },
      "name": "text - 10"
    },
